h3cVoiceAnalogInterface.name: h3cVoiceAnalogInterface

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

h3cVoiceAnalogInterface.contactinfo: PLAT Team Huawei 3Com Technologies co.,Ltd. Shang-Di Information Industry Base, Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:100085
h3cVoiceAnalogInterface.description: The MIB file is to provide the definition of the general analog voice interface configuration.

h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgTable.name: h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgTable
h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgTable.description: This table contains the information about configurable parameters for an voice analog interface.

h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgEntry.name: h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgEntry
h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgEntry.description: The entry of h3cVoAnalogIfCommonCfgTable, which is automatically created when an analog voice module has been found.

h3cVoAIfCfgPortIndex.name: h3cVoAIfCfgPortIndex
h3cVoAIfCfgPortIndex.description: The index of a voice analog interface common configuration table.

h3cVoAIfCfgPortType.name: h3cVoAIfCfgPortType
h3cVoAIfCfgPortType.description: This object indicates the type of a voice analog interface.

h3cVoAIfCfgPortSubLine.description: This object indicates the port subscriber line name.

h3cVoAIfFXOCfgSubLine.description: This object indicates the port subscriber line name.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerPortIndex.description: The index of voice analog interface fxo timer table.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerDtmfInterval.description: This object indicates DTMF(Dual Tone Multi-Frequency) sending interval in milliseconds.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerDialInterval.description: The interval, in seconds, between two dialing numbers.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerFirstDial.description: The period of time, in seconds, before dialing the first number.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerRingBack.description: This object indicates the maximum duration the ring back to persist. Unit is second.

h3cVoAIfFXOTimerSubLine.description: This object indicates the port subscriber line name.

h3cVoAnalogIfEMCfgEntry.description: The entry of h3cVoAnalogIfEMCfgTable, which is automatically created when an analog EM voice module has been found.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgPortIndex.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgPortIndex
h3cVoAIfEMCfgPortIndex.description: The index of voice analog interface EM configuration table.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode
h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode.description: This object indicates the signal modes of an analog EM interfaces.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyParm.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyParm
h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyParm.description: This object indicates the operation of an analog EM signal.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyType.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyType
h3cVoAIfEMCfgPhyType.description: This object indicates the EM type of the analog interface.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutRing.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutRing
h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutRing.description: The maximum seconds, to wait for the ring back on the EM interface.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutWaitDigit.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutWaitDigit
h3cVoAIfEMCfgTimeoutWaitDigit.description: The maximum length of time, in seconds, to wait for called number on an analog EM interface.

h3cVoAIfEMCfgSubLine.name: h3cVoAIfEMCfgSubLine
h3cVoAIfEMCfgSubLine.description: This object indicates the port subscriber line name.

h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable.name: h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable
h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable.description: This table contains the timer information for an analog EM interface.

h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry.name: h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry
h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry.description: The entry of h3cVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable, which is automatically created when an analog EM voice module has been found.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerPortIndex.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerPortIndex
h3cVoAIfEMTimerPortIndex.description: The index of voice analog interface EM timer table.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmf.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmf
h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmf.description: This object indicates DTMF(Dual Tone Multi-Frequency) sending duration in milliseconds.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmfInterval.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmfInterval
h3cVoAIfEMTimerDtmfInterval.description: This object indicates DTMF(Dual Tone Multi-Frequency) sending interval in milliseconds.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerSendWink.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerSendWink
h3cVoAIfEMTimerSendWink.description: This object indicates the maximum time in milliseconds between receiving seizure signal and sending wink signal. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'winkStart'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkRising.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkRising
h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkRising.description: This object indicates the maximum time in milliseconds between sending seizure signal and receiving wink signal. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'winkStart'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkHold.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkHold
h3cVoAIfEMTimerWinkHold.description: This object indicates the maximum duration in milliseconds to send wink signal. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'winkStart'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerDialoutDelay.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerDialoutDelay
h3cVoAIfEMTimerDialoutDelay.description: This object indicates the maximum duration in milliseconds to send called digits. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'immediateDial'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayRising.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayRising
h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayRising.description: This object indicates the maximum duration in milliseconds between receiveing seizure signal and sending delay signal. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'delayDial'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayHold.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayHold
h3cVoAIfEMTimerDelayHold.description: This object indicates the maximum duration in milliseconds to send delay signal. This object can only take effect when h3cVoAIfEMCfgSignalMode is set to 'delayDial'.

h3cVoAIfEMTimerSubLine.name: h3cVoAIfEMTimerSubLine
h3cVoAIfEMTimerSubLine.description: This object indicates the port subscriber line name.
